<br>
At least one or two people mentioned that but never confirmed, dunno. Flowing thought II should be in the sp.dat file, does it confirm a +2 mana regen? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uremfin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Remfin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/16/01 11:59:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Scepter of Al'Kabor as a testing tool?</span><hr size=1> They promised chanters over a month ago there would NEVER be an item with more than flowing thought 2's current effect (at the time, 2 mana/tick and still is)<br>
